WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:09:02.668 --> 00:09:05.420
<i>This dam project
will create many new jobs.</i>

3
00:09:05.629 --> 00:09:10.676
The Party and country
will assist in your relocation.

4
00:09:12.594 --> 00:09:14.096
Grandma. give me your hand.

5
00:09:14.638 --> 00:09:17.015
- But where are they taking us?
- It'll be all right.

6
00:09:22.479 --> 00:09:23.522
Brother!

7
00:09:24.189 --> 00:09:26.316
Grandma. I will send you money.

8
00:09:32.573 --> 00:09:33.657
Who can write?

9
00:09:34.449 --> 00:09:35.784
Who can read?

10
00:09:37.286 --> 00:09:38.495
Who can weld?

11
00:10:49.608 --> 00:10:53.445
I put a lot of faith
into your organization.

12
00:10:55.113 --> 00:10:57.866
It's a perfect replica. Roland.

13
00:10:58.033 --> 00:11:01.203
There are too many fanatics out there
that could damage her.

14
00:11:01.954 --> 00:11:06.465
Just think about the beautiful Buddha 
statues they blew up in Afghanistan.

15
00:11:06.750 --> 00:11:10.812
Our Heritage Organization
has already made selections...

16
00:11:10.963 --> 00:11:13.799
...from the British Museum
and L'Hermitage.

17
00:11:21.139 --> 00:11:23.976
I guess she'll be safe now.
tucked away...

18
00:11:24.434 --> 00:11:29.147
...hidden in some bunker
in Switzerland.

19
00:11:30.107 --> 00:11:33.110
Perfectly safe. Roland.

20
00:11:34.278 --> 00:11:37.155
Only infrared analysis
would reveal the difference.

21
00:11:38.866 --> 00:11:40.534
But it's still a fake.

22
00:16:41.710 --> 00:16:42.750
Hello?

23
00:16:43.211 --> 00:16:44.586
<i>Laura!</i>

24
00:16:45.339 --> 00:16:46.757
<i>Laura. can you hear me?</i>

25
00:16:47.090 --> 00:16:48.634
Roland. is that you?

26
00:16:48.800 --> 00:16:50.761
<i>Laura. they lied to us.</i>

27
00:16:50.928 --> 00:16:53.138
I've arranged a press
conference for tomorrow.

28
00:16:53.305 --> 00:16:55.724
I will tell everyone the truth
about what's going on.

29
00:16:55.891 --> 00:16:57.392
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

30
00:16:57.601 --> 00:16:59.144
The art you collected...

31
00:16:59.853 --> 00:17:01.522
...it's not in the Alps.

32
00:17:01.688 --> 00:17:03.106
<i>Those tunnels are empty.</i>

33
00:17:03.273 --> 00:17:04.316
<i>I have proof!</i>

34
00:17:06.151 --> 00:17:07.277
Laura.

35
00:17:07.444 --> 00:17:08.612
Laura. can you hear me?

36
00:17:09.363 --> 00:17:12.324
- I'm losing you. Roland?
- Laura. can you hear me?

37
00:39:02.426 --> 00:39:04.970
- Yuri!
- Zultan!

38
00:39:05.137 --> 00:39:07.222
I feared you would not come.

39
00:39:18.609 --> 00:39:20.402
Zultan. listen to me...

40
00:39:20.569 --> 00:39:23.572
...we are fighters.
we never go down...

41
00:39:24.489 --> 00:39:27.492
...no matter how hard they hit us.

42
00:39:30.078 --> 00:39:31.205
Kill the bastard.

43
00:39:31.788 --> 00:39:34.625
Kill the bastard. Zultan.

44
00:40:13.872 --> 00:40:15.624
Yuri. where are you going?

45
01:19:19.843 --> 01:19:23.722
<i>Do not believe in something simply
because you have heard it. Nima.</i>

46
01:19:25.140 --> 01:19:27.935
But. great Lama.
Tenzin is my brother.

47
01:19:28.977 --> 01:19:31.939
He works inside the big tunnel.
where the ships are built.

48
01:19:35.067 --> 01:19:39.530
But what is there in your wisdom.
great Lama. if Tenzin is right?

49
01:19:40.239 --> 01:19:42.616
What if our world
is indeed coming to an end?

50
01:19:52.918 --> 01:19:54.058
It is full. great Rinpoche.

51
01:19:54.082 --> 01:19:55.082
It is full.

52
01:19:56.912 --> 01:19:58.011
It's full!

53
01:20:01.927 --> 01:20:03.053
Like this cup...

54
01:20:03.220 --> 01:20:07.683
...you are full of opinions
and speculations.

55
01:20:09.601 --> 01:20:11.353
To see the light of wisdom...

56
01:20:11.770 --> 01:20:14.606
...you first must empty your cup.

57
01:20:32.249 --> 01:20:33.709
Be careful with the clutch.

58
01:20:34.543 --> 01:20:36.545
It tends to slip.

59
01:20:54.688 --> 01:20:57.733
- Grandma.
- Grandpa. Nima is here!

60
01:20:58.400 --> 01:21:00.277
Grandma.
I got a message from Tenzin.

61
01:21:00.485 --> 01:21:03.405
He wants us to meet him
in Cho Ming at the west gate.

62
01:21:04.072 --> 01:21:07.117
He says he can get us on the ships
he's working on.

63
01:21:07.993 --> 01:21:11.330
What are you talking about?
Tenzin works on the dam.

64
01:21:14.666 --> 01:21:16.251
Grandma...

65
01:21:16.835 --> 01:21:17.876
...the dam is a ship!

66
01:21:18.529 --> 01:21:20.255
The government lied to us.

67
01:21:20.380 --> 01:21:22.466
There will be a big flood!

68
01:21:23.300 --> 01:21:24.760
We must pack up right away.

69
01:21:26.094 --> 01:21:27.804
Nima. he gave you the truck?

70
01:21:28.555 --> 01:21:31.517
We took a trip
on the Laem Song ferry once.

71
01:21:32.559 --> 01:21:34.853
Grandpa threw up the whole way.

72
01:21:36.355 --> 01:21:37.606
Let's eat first.

73
01:55:30.639 --> 01:55:31.723
Who are they?

74
01:55:32.182 --> 01:55:33.851
We found them along side
of the road.

75
01:55:34.268 --> 01:55:35.310
Send them back!

76
01:55:41.817 --> 01:55:43.402
I am a follower...

77
01:55:44.403 --> 01:55:46.071
...of our great Lama Rinpoche.

78
01:55:46.780 --> 01:55:48.323
You know I cannot do that.

79
01:56:25.777 --> 01:56:29.573
We are all children of the earth.

80
01:56:29.865 --> 01:56:33.368
My plan will not work
for so many. Grandma.

81
01:56:33.535 --> 01:56:37.414
We will take them all.

82
01:57:34.054 --> 01:57:35.180
We have to hurry!

83
01:57:35.681 --> 01:57:36.849
They are leaving!

84
01:57:55.659 --> 01:57:56.660
Tenzin wait!

85
01:57:58.203 --> 01:58:00.372
Grandma. we're almost there.

86
01:58:35.365 --> 01:58:36.408
Mr. President.

87
01:58:37.451 --> 01:58:38.493
You've got to see this.

88
01:59:49.356 --> 01:59:51.692
Down there Oleg. you go first!

89
02:00:28.061 --> 02:00:29.354
Daddy look!

90
02:10:59.109 --> 02:11:00.986
Tenzin. almost there.

91
02:11:02.112 --> 02:11:03.655
Nima. what happened?

92
02:18:19.007 --> 02:18:20.424
Grandma. Grandpa.

93
02:18:20.925 --> 02:18:22.593
I'm sorry.

94
02:18:22.969 --> 02:18:27.099
- I could not save us.
- He has gone back in. He will fix it.

95
02:18:28.225 --> 02:18:30.477
There's no way.

96
02:18:31.520 --> 02:18:33.522
Don't lose your faith. brother.

97
02:37:42.759 --> 02:37:44.760
English

98
